---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Number7" description="Number 7 Cognition LLP is a small studio building the agents the next billion people will use without calling them agents.">
  <section class="subhero"><div class="container">
    <div class="crumbs">Home / About</div>
    <h1 class="serif">We don't want AI to be aspirational. We want it to be Tuesday.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Number 7 Cognition LLP is a small studio building the agents the next billion people will use without calling them agents. Seven countries. One cadence. We release every Friday.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="about"><div class="container">
    <p class="thesis serif">Our thesis is boring on purpose. The software industry has spent two years rehearsing what AI could be. We prefer invoices, calls, meetings, and classrooms — the boring, weekly rhythms of real work — because that's where AI becomes electricity. Not a demo. An outlet.</p>

    <h2 class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">How we work.</h2>
    <div class="how">
      <div><h4>Ship Friday.</h4><p>Weekly releases. No exceptions. The only valid excuse is a production incident.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Write first.</h4><p>Every feature starts as a 1-pager. If it can't survive prose, it can't survive production.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Measure in outcomes.</h4><p>Hours reclaimed, tickets closed, calls screened. Vanity metrics don't ship.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Pair with customers.</h4><p>Design partners sit in our standups. Their Jira and ours share a label.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Stay lean.</h4><p>We'd rather raise the quality bar than the headcount.</p></div>
      <div><h4>Leave a trail.</h4><p>Every agent run writes an auditable log. No black boxes, ever.</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 id="newsroom" class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">What we're building toward.</h2>
    <p class="thesis serif" style="margin-top:16px">The next billion people will meet AI the way they meet electricity: everyday, unremarkable, already on. That's the bar. Keynotes don't clear it. Invoices, calls, classrooms, tasks, and meetings do.</p>

    <h2 id="careers" class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">Careers.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted); max-width:640px; margin-top:8px">We don't post job descriptions. We post problems. If one of them is yours, tell us how you'd solve it. Write to <a href="mailto:careers@number7.io">careers@number7.io</a> with a 300-word sketch — we'll reply in 48 hours.</p>

    <h2 class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">The team.</h2>
    <div class="team team-two">
      <div class="person">
        <div class="name"><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/phani-marupaka" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Phani Marupaka</a></div>
        <div class="role">Co-founder</div>
      </div>
      <div class="person">
        <div class="name"><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/premsaimanne" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Prem Sai Manne</a></div>
        <div class="role">Co-founder</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">Where we are.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted); max-width:640px; margin-top:8px">India (headquartered in Hyderabad) · UAE · Qatar · Singapore · Zimbabwe · USA · UK.</p>

    <h2 id="press" class="serif" style="margin-top:60px; font-size:28px">Press.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted); max-width:640px; margin-top:8px">For press inquiries, write to <a href="mailto:press@number7.io">press@number7.io</a>. Brand kit available on request.</p>
  </div></section>
</Base>
